attempt_description:
A string composed of a and b, where:

- All a's appear individually or in the form of ba;
- All b's appear individually or in the form of ab;
- The string can optionally end with an a.

The first half is composed of repeated single a or ba (no consecutive aa allowed);

The middle may optionally contain one bb (but no other forms of consecutive b allowed);

The second half is composed of repeated single a or ab (no consecutive bb allowed).
